SPECKit Plus is an AI-driven project development framework that helps teams build software in a structured, predictable, and efficient way. It guides developers through defining the project vision, specifying requirements, planning execution, breaking down tasks, and implementing the final solution. It ensures clarity, reduces confusion, and improves collaboration between developers and AI agents.

